title: Lynne Lorraine's
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, American, Fast food, Juice bar, Take-out, Catering
description: A juice and smoothie bar with a grab n go menu that ranges from breakfast bowls and wraps to salads and sweets. Makes in-house the peanut butter, almond butter, and almond milk. Juice is made fresh to order. Est. 2014 in the Five Points area of East Nashville. Has free Wi-Fi.
